---
import Link from './icons/Link.astro'
---

<header>
  <h1 class='mb-6 animate-intro font-semibold'>Surya Nallaparaju</h1>
  <div class='flex flex-col gap-y-3.5'>
    <p
      class='animate-intro font-light leading-snug opacity-0 [animation-delay:0.2s]'
    >
      I'm an MTech Computer Science student (currently) at NIT Warangal. This is my lil
      corner of the web where I share my work with y'all.
    </p>
    <div
      class='flex animate-intro items-center font-light opacity-0 [animation-delay:0.25s]'
    >

    </div>
    <p class='animate-intro font-light opacity-0 [animation-delay:0.3s]'>
      In my free time, I spend time outdoors, listen to podcasts and music, eat (a lot), and tinker
      around with all sorts of random computer stuff.
    </p>

    <!-- Clean Navigation -->
    <nav class="mt-6 animate-intro opacity-0 [animation-delay:0.35s]">
      <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-x-6 gap-y-2">
        <a
          href="/blog/"
          class="group flex items-center gap-1 font-medium text-neutral-700 transition-all hover:text-yellow-600 hover:translate-x-1"
        >
          <span>Blog</span>
          <div class="opacity-0 group-hover:opacity-100 transition-opacity">
            <Link />
          </div>
        </a>
        <a
          href="/gallery/"
          class="group flex items-center gap-1 font-medium text-neutral-700 transition-all hover:text-blue-600 hover:translate-x-1"
        >
          <span>Gallery</span>
          <div class="opacity-0 group-hover:opacity-100 transition-opacity">
            <Link />
          </div>
        </a>
        <a
          href="/resume.pdf"
          class="group flex items-center gap-1 font-medium text-neutral-700 transition-all hover:text-green-600 hover:translate-x-1"
        >
          <span>Resume</span>
          <div class="opacity-0 group-hover:opacity-100 transition-opacity">
            <Link />
          </div>
        </a>
      </div>
    </nav>
  </div>
</header>